{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 728, "title": "Reuse `__interactivehook__` to initialize `readline` or `libedit`", "body": "Fixes https://github.com/inducer/pudb/issues/726\r\nReplaces https://github.com/inducer/pudb/pull/727\r\n\r\n[`__interactivehook__`](https://github.com/python/cpython/blob/185a6e942af3e44b3bdb2bdcf2d55c0a6208f89b/Lib/site.py#L487) supports `libedit` from [version 3.4](https://github.com/python/cpython/blob/1f08c772f5a68bdf8309d6ad1cdddb838fc35feb/Lib/site.py#L475-L480).\r\n\r\nUsers might also customize their hooks and expect that to work in `pudb` shell as well.\r\n\r\nI've tested that with pythons 3.8..3.15 and it works fine.\r\nEven history files are not messed up since `pudb.shell.run_classic_shell` overrides history configuration set by `__interactivehook__`.", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "7214fa7dbd27e7b53fd1ba88a821d981d458c69c", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "inducer/pudb"}, "url": "https://github.com/inducer/pudb/pull/728", "createdAt": "2026-02-17T21:17:16Z", "mergedAt": "2026-02-18T23:36:28Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "inducer/pudb"}, "sha": "7214fa7dbd27e7b53fd1ba88a821d981d458c69c"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/inducer/pudb/pull/728.diff", "number": 728, "created_at": "2026-02-17T21:17:16Z", "merged_at": "2026-02-18T23:36:28Z", "resolved_issues": [726]}
